### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### Message Save - TEXT
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-001",
  "senderId": "user-a",
  "messageType": "TEXT",
  "content": "hello redis caching gateway",
  "metadataJson": null,
  "sentAt": "2026-03-14T17:00:00"
}

### Message Save - IMAGE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-002",
  "senderId": "user-b",
  "messageType": "IMAGE",
  "content": null,
  "metadataJson": "{\"url\":\"https://example.com/sample-image.jpg\",\"fileName\":\"sample-image.jpg\"}",
  "sentAt": "2026-03-14T17:01:00"
}

### Message Save - FILE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "msg-003",
  "senderId": "user-a",
  "messageType": "FILE",
  "content": null,
  "metadataJson": "{\"url\":\"https://example.com/manual.pdf\",\"fileName\":\"manual.pdf\",\"size\":123456}",
  "sentAt": "2026-03-14T17:02:00"
}

### Get Recent Messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages?limit=50

### Get Messages Before
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages?before=2026-03-14T17:10:00&limit=20

### Get Messages After
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/messages?after=2026-03-14T16:59:00&limit=20

### Get Conversation Meta
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/conv-001/meta

### Get Not Found Conversation Meta
GET http://localhost:8080/api/conversations/not-found/meta